.TH "LIGHTNING-WALLET-ACCOUNTS-SUMMARY" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-wallet-accounts-summary \- aggregate balance totals across all wallet accounts
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning wallet-accounts-summary
.SH DESCRIPTION
Queries the wallet SQLite database and returns aggregate statistics
across all accounts.
.PP
Output:
.nf
{"wallet":"...","account_count":N,
 "total_balance_sat":N,"total_limit_sat":N}
.fi
Returns
.nf
{"error":"database_not_found"}
.fi
when the wallet database does not exist.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning-wallet-stats (1),
.BR lightning-wallet-check (1)
